<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Seattle Times 1997 TOC</TITLE>
<META name="description" content="1996 Columns Table of Contents">
<META name="keywords" content="FREE, Knight-Ridder, Seattle Times, Columns, Op-Eds, 1997">
</HEAD><BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF" BACKGROUND="/free/Images/bluewhite_paper.gif"><IMG SRC = "/free/Images/flogo.gif" ALT = "">
<P>Knight-Ridder Columns</P>
<TABLE CELLSPACING=2 CELLPADDING=1><CAPTION><H2>As appearing in the <CITE>Seattle Times</CITE></H2>
</CAPTION>
<UL>
<TR>
	<TD><LI><A HREF="Cows.ST1997.html">Cowboys of the Old West Need to Clean Up Their Act</A></TD><TD> January 22, 1997</TD>
</TR>
<TR>
	<TD><LI><A HREF="Wolf1.ST1997.html">A Place for Wild Wolves and a Reason to Kill Them</A></TD><TD> January 8, 1997</TD>
</TR></UL>
</TABLE>
