<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>News Division - Media Research Center</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/mrc/images/back-news-test.gif">
<blockquote>
<center>
<a href="/mrc/images/hdr-news.map"><img border="0" src="/mrc/images/hdr-news.gif" ISMAP></a>
</center>
<br><br>
<ul>
<P>
<ul>
<li><a href="/mrc/news/about.html">About MRC's News Division</a>
<LI>JUST RELEASED!! The Ninth Annual Awards for the Year's Worst Reporting: <a href="/mrc/nq/best/96nqbst.html">The Best <I>Notable Quotables</I> of 1996</a>.
<LI><a href="/mrc/reality/">Media Reality Check '96</a> -- Did reporters really cover the elections objectively?
<li><a href="/mrc/cyberalert/">MRC Cyber Alert Messages about Media Bias</a>
<LI>NEW BOOK: <a href="/mrc/bookstore/"><i>Pattern of Deception: The Media's Role in the Clinton Presidency</i></a>
<LI><a href="/mrc/mediawatch/"><i>MediaWatch</i></a>
<li><a href="/mrc/nq/"><i>Notable Quotables</i></a>
