The following audio clips are from President Reagan's remarks at National Review's 30th Anniversary party held<br> December 5, 1985 at the Plaza Hotel in New York City. We are making them available in two formats in order to accomodate those lacking a RealAudio Player, and also to satisfy visitors who are willing to wait for the higher<br>
quality sound of a WAV file to download.<P>
