<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/nationalreview/endbox.html 204.71.237.88 19970208080651 text/html 10434
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 08:07:35 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 07-Feb-97 23:38:51 GMT
Content-length: 10248
