<DOCOLDNO>IA091-000980-B041-26</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/savers/library/advis26.html 204.71.237.88 19970208081152 text/html 9703
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 08:12:34 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 15-Apr-96 15:23:19 GMT
Content-length: 9518
