href="/savers/legislation/blcusa.html">Summary</a>) USA Tax Act of 1995
<br>
<li>Mr. Shelby - <a href="/savers/legislation/s1050.html">S.1050</a> or (<a 
href="/savers/legislation/blcflat.html">Summary</a>) Freedom and Fairness 
Restoration Act of 1995 (aka: Flat Tax) <br>
<li>Mr. Specter - <a href="/savers/legislation/s488.html">S. 488</a> Flat tax on 
earned income.<br>
</ul>
<p>
<hr>
[<a href="/savers/">Home</a>], Legislation Listed By: [<a 
href="/savers/legnum.html">Bill No.</a>]<br>
<font size=2>Savers &amp; Investors League, September 1996</font>
</body>  </html>

