<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/heritage/library/categories/regulation/fyi129.html 204.71.237.88 19970208082603 text/html 29135
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 08:26:40 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 05-Feb-97 14:50:48 GMT
