<p>
<hr>
<p>
<li>Of Canadian patients waiting for health care under their national health care system, <font color="blue"><b>percent that say they are in pain</b></font>: 
<p>
<center><font color="red"><h3>45%</h3></font>
</center>
<p>
<FONT SIZE=2>Source: Statistics Canada</FONT>
</ol> <p>
