Since you are not using <a href="http://www.netscape.com">Netscape</a>, your 
responses can not be encrypted. So if there is any private information that 
you don't want to make known, feel free to call our toll-free number at 
1-800-225-4008 to place your subscription. Otherwise, please continue your 
subscription below. 
<p>
<a href="/townhall/FRC/subscribe/subscribe-u.html">Continue Subscription</a>
<p>
If you want to unsubscribe from one of our E-Mail Subscription lists, visit 
our <a href="/townhall/listserv/FRC/welcome.html">Cancel Subscription</a> 
screen.<p>



